column2: SELECT    m.objid, c.identifier, m.objid, m.ra, m.dec, m.run, m.camcol, m.field,    m.gain_g, m.gain_i, m.gain_r, m.gain_u, m.gain_z,    m.kk_g, m.kk_i, m.kk_r, m.kk_u, m.kk_z,    m.airmass_g, m.airmass_i, m.airmass_r, m.airmass_u, m.airmass_z,    m.aa_g, m.aa_i, m.aa_r, m.aa_u, m.aa_z,    m.seeing_g, m.seeing_i, m.seeing_r, m.seeing_u, m.seeing_z into MyDB.new_#_corr FROM MyDB.new_# AS m 	JOIN MyDB.new_#_id_coord as c ON c.ra=m.ra AND c.dec=m.dec
